# spec.tasks — PitchTwin

> Regenerated from `spec.plan` + `spec.arch` + `spec.harness-brainstorm.md`, then
> re-grounded to the **`main`** branch (the base for this worktree). On `main` all
> agents already call `llm_client.call_json()` uniformly — there is **no
> `pydantic_ai` second path and no `logfire`** — so the harness is a clean unifying
> layer and tracing is **console-based**. PHASE 2.5 is the Agent Harness (issue #1)
> and is now implemented.

