## Agent Ownership Map

| Agent | File | LLM path | Output schema |
|---|---|---|---|
| Harness | `agents/harness.py` | — | — |
| Schemas | `agents/schemas.py` | — | — |
| Profile | `agents/profile_agent.py` | harness · json | `ProfileOutput` |
| Client Research | `agents/client_research_agent.py` | harness · json | `ClientContextOutput` |
| Matching | `agents/matching_agent.py` | harness · json | `MatchingOutput` |
| Writer | `agents/writer_agent.py` | harness · json | `WriterOutput` |
| Gap | `agents/gap_agent.py` | harness · json | `GapAnalysisOutput` |
| Combined | `agents/combined_agent.py` | harness · json | `CombinedOutput` |
| Debrief | `agents/debrief_agent.py` | harness · json | `DebriefOutput` |
| Persona | `agents/persona_agent.py` | harness · text | — |

